{"tid":877753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜首場造勢晚會湧進三萬人 陸橋也擠爆","createTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T02:24:29.000Z","uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf474fb77879936eb5fa2bfaac9c2bd4af64a20","tid":877753,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://video.udn.com/embed/news/962295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.udn.com%2Fembed%2Fnews%2F962295&d=YBcb6ut74pg%2FTCPERw5jnywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1ad1ce0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.udn.com/embed/news/962295</a><br />\n選戰進入最後一個月，韓國瑜首場大型造勢會今晚登場，會場旗海飄揚，參與群眾號稱5萬人之多，盛大場面感動不少支持者。韓國瑜不斷以「偉大的高雄市民」稱呼支持者，期盼高雄市民展現素質，一起證明高雄是民主聖地。<br />\n<br />\n為讓韓國瑜的「空戰」聲量轉化為「陸戰」實力，前立法院長王金平發起「韓國瑜三山之友會」造勢活動，首場從鳳山出發，支持群眾參與踴躍，造勢活動導致鄰近交通打結，晚會邀請立委蔣萬安、柯志恩、王育敏與江啟臣等人演講。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市農會理事長蕭漢俊表示，韓國瑜被對手譏笑只有空戰沒有陸戰，王金平是高雄縣出身，政壇上只有他夠分量來召集高雄鄉親，所以由王金平帶頭打組織戰，讓韓國瑜當空軍總司令，王金平當陸軍總司令，「造勢晚會是空軍與陸軍大會師」。<br />\n<br />\n晚間8點，韓國瑜與前立法院長王金平一起進場，因現場群眾大熱情，韓國瑜的上衣被熱情群眾拉扯掀起，上台後抽空整理服裝，主持人一度打斷王金平致詞，希望擠在舞台前的民眾可以後退預留空間，避免發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n王金平表示，韓國瑜被綠營認為只靠電視與網路打「空戰」，從鳳山開始，支持者都當陸戰部隊，一個人是一顆小石，一起支持大石（韓國瑜），形成小山丘越過鳳山，之後一路挺進旗山與岡山。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜登場後，連續三次以「偉大的高雄市人民」向現場群眾問好，現場氣氛沸騰，「凍蒜」之聲久久不停。韓國瑜表示，高雄有山有海，2、30年卻沒有好好發展經濟，偉大的高雄市民應該要清醒了，以前高雄是最富庶的城市，許多外地人來工作，今天我們的孩子卻必須往遠方飄去，因為沒有足夠的工作提供孩子養份，市府有責任讓農漁民過好日子，若順利當選，明年二月帶領大家去外面搶訂單。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜說，以後高雄會張開臂膀，用熱情迎接所有城市、國家 ，鄰近國家都在進步，沒有人等高雄，「自己的高雄自己救、自己的未來自己拚」。非常期待這場選舉乾淨、健康，自己靠一瓶礦泉水選到底，若因此贏得勝利，代表高雄市民偉大，證明高雄是民主聖地、選民素質最棒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/26/realtime/5448716.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2Frealtime%2F5448716.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=b6f576e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部分支持者站在制高點觀看造勢活動。記者劉學聖／攝影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/26/realtime/5448717.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2Frealtime%2F5448717.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=796b6121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國瑜的襯衫在進場時遭熱情群眾掀起，上台後當眾整理衣服。記者劉學聖／攝影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/26/realtime/5448718.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2Frealtime%2F5448718.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=b067ad9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會場旗海飄揚，支持者不斷揮舞國旗喊「凍蒜」。記者劉學聖／攝影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/26/realtime/5448719.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2Frealtime%2F5448719.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=7ff9ba57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空拍畫面場面盛大，造勢會場被支持者擠得水洩不通。圖／韓國瑜競選總部提供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/26/realtime/5448720.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2Frealtime%2F5448720.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=1ec27764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王金平（左）與韓國瑜（中）一起進場，現場氣氛沸騰。記者劉學聖／攝影"},{"pid":"068e509621f9349eb988831e984cbb0cf2366be6","tid":877753,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"條友呢排好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869940ddd4024417969599613d3123cf4eedcf88","tid":877753,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068e509621f9349eb988831e984cbb0cf2366be6","tid":877753,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"條友呢排好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"好&quot;紅&quot;"},{"pid":"a6363fb5ff3c2ea9c71a05cbb2c79e0611224d3c","tid":877753,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b8cfc9b59674ef30b9c46e204b9cbe2b1dec8d7","tid":877753,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T00:57:50.000Z","msg":"高雄》韓國瑜晚間首場大型造勢 台中支持者搶頭香占位！<br />\n<br />\n高雄三山挺韓國瑜之友會鳳山場26日晚間即將登場，這是韓國瑜首次大型造勢，指標意義重大，主辦單位正在準備場地，現場排放1萬張椅凳，活動晚間6點半才開始，竟有遠從台中來的支持者一大早搭客運到場搶頭香，中午過後也陸續有民眾準備入場，韓國瑜預告，「有信心晚會人數會非常非常多」。<br />\n<br />\n來自台中大肚區的陳先生、李先生說，看了中天政論節目獲知韓國瑜要辦大型造勢，26日早上8點，兩人便搭乘國光客運到高雄，再轉捷運前往鳳山會場，不到12點就坐在入口處等待，中午前往的高雄在地支持者以為自己很早到，沒想到頭香已被2位老先生搶占。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">主辦單位透露，光是農會、黨部系統動員遊覽車就超過200輛，加上自發性前往的支持者，場面預計會非常浩大。</span><br />\n<br />\n「大姑娘進洞房，頭一遭，第一場大型造勢，有信心人數會非常非常多！」韓國瑜上午接受媒體訪問時表示，這次高雄三山挺韓國瑜之友會，是農民團體自己運作、聯繫的，當然會有遊覽車載人來，但他重申希望所有動員都能尊重他的承諾，通通只有1瓶礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，「後援會」是候選人陣營所主導成立，但「之友會」沒有任何物資支援、沒有任何指令，「只要願意相挺的來邀請我，我就去，但請大家尊重候選人對於這次乾淨選舉的決定」。<br />\n(中時 )"},{"pid":"06086e40cd6c127a20989e6866f32c1da20bd23e","tid":877753,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:00:48.000Z","msg":"Never kmt"},{"pid":"495040b9772e2592811000b9f58b0c1bd777c2fe","tid":877753,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"韓國人？"},{"pid":"52d967c27b8d450c26084bd54691d63065e631fb","tid":877753,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:05:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4b3eecbb1a10e0acf6dc2919d78070af5413178","tid":877753,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"068e509621f9349eb988831e984cbb0cf2366be6","tid":877753,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"條友呢排好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:07:47.000Z","msg":"依條癲佬黎<br />\n前排咁啱去左趟高雄<br />\n見到佢嗰宣傳海報寫要令高雄成為全台最有米嘅地方<br />\n我企係高雄街頭望住個海報真係笑左黎聲...<br />\n鳩噏當秘笈..."},{"pid":"c0210763f2ea5a716dbe3d432bd7486453cf1365","tid":877753,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d24eb0eacd85920e7fdf9418b3b5ebea688efb0","tid":877753,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0210763f2ea5a716dbe3d432bd7486453cf1365","tid":877753,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4b3eecbb1a10e0acf6dc2919d78070af5413178","tid":877753,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"068e509621f9349eb988831e984cbb0cf2366be6","tid":877753,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"條友呢排好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:07:47.000Z","msg":"依條癲佬黎<br />\n前排咁啱去左趟高雄<br />\n見到佢嗰宣傳海報寫要令高雄成為全台最有米嘅地方<br />\n我企係高雄街頭望住個海報真係笑左黎聲...<br />\n鳩噏當秘笈..."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"問准美爸爸未"},{"pid":"7f22cd9f6f8d003556f795f783e4ded8e41545f5","tid":877753,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0210763f2ea5a716dbe3d432bd7486453cf1365","tid":877753,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4b3eecbb1a10e0acf6dc2919d78070af5413178","tid":877753,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"068e509621f9349eb988831e984cbb0cf2366be6",